Carol Vorderman, 62, took to Instagram to show off her ultra-toned figure as she showed off her gym routine. The former Countdown star sported royal blue leggings paired with a white long-sleeved crop top, leaving her toned abs on full display. Carol highlighted her ultra-slim waist in the workout number, while also telling her fans about her gym routine. She captioned the post in view of her 313,000 followers: "YM SESH FIRST THING WITH @meldeane12. Slamming,, lunging, lifting, stretching, sweating, "Can hardly walk but so so happy. I've missed the gym for a few months.....back now....booommmmmm. "Off to work now.....BBC RADIO WALES....and then some secret filming.....Ooooofffffff." (sic)